SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5903
A bill to amend 1974 PA 258, entitled
"Mental health code,"
by amending section 134 (MCL 330.1134), as amended by 2015 PA 59.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 134. (1) The director shall establish a comprehensive
2 system of licensing for psychiatric hospitals and psychiatric units
3 in the this state to protect the public by ensuring that these
4 psychiatric hospitals and psychiatric units provide the facilities
5 and the ancillary supporting services necessary to maintain a high
6 quality of patient care. Separate criteria shall must be developed
7 for licensing hospital beds for minors.
8 (2) A psychiatric hospital or psychiatric unit licensed to
9 provide both adult and minor psychiatric inpatient services may use
